{"type":"assistant","message":{"model":"claude-opus-4-6","id":"msg_0176rEsGL1LUPyXaaz2Db8Df","type":"message","role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"Now I have a thorough understanding of the improvement plan and the codebase. Let me decompose the plan into tasks. The key dependencies are:\n\n1. Food dictionary (new file) - foundation for Pattern 1, 2, 7\n2. OCR repair function using dictionary - depends on 1, needed for Pattern 1, 2, 7\n3. Apply OCR repair before scoring - depends on 2, fixes Pattern 2\n4. Garbled text detection improvements - independent, fixes Pattern 7\n5. Candidate-relative position bonus - independent, fixes Pattern 3\n6. Title-absent page detection - independent, fixes Pattern 4\n\n\n7. Compound title dedup protection - independent, fixes Pattern 5\n8. Cooking verb expansion with bilingual support - independent, fixes Pattern 6\n\nI'm ordering these tasks by their dependencies, starting with the foundation work and then moving through the independent improvements.\n\n1. Task 01: Create food dictionary file (new file, foundation)\n2. Task 02: Dictionary-guided OCR repair function (depends on 01, modifies title-extractor.ts)\n3. Task 03: Apply OCR repair before candidate scoring (depends on 02)\n4. Task 04: Strengthen garbled-text detection (pipe-in-word, mixed-script) - independent\n5. Task 05: Candidate-relative position bonus + first-after-preamble bonus (independent)\n6. Task 06: Title-absent page detection (independent)\n7. Task 07: Compound title dedup protection with MAIN RECIPE / --VARIATION filtering (independent)\n8. Task 08: Expand cooking verbs and boost bilingual layout patterns (independent)\n\nTasks 4 through 8 can mostly be tackled independently of each other, though they'll all benefit from the OCR repair foundation being in place. The first three tasks need to happen in sequence since each builds on the previous one. Now I'm ready to start writing out these task files.","signature":""}],"stop_reason":null,"stop_sequence":null,"usage":{"input_tokens":1,"cache_creation_input_tokens":230,"cache_read_input_tokens":33606,"cache_creation":{"ephemeral_5m_input_tokens":0,"ephemeral_1h_input_tokens":230},"output_tokens":8,"service_tier":"standard","inference_geo":"not_available"},"context_management":null},"parent_tool_use_id":null,"session_id":"992d880b-e463-4199-be8a-c9ca68db2e09","uuid":"a396f497-8d8d-4013-9535-98ab8c9317fe"}
